moji\" /> <br />\n但見而家身邊d朋友全部都有女有事業 有d仲plan緊結婚 開始覺得唔可以再係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然而家都失緊業 不過都努力培養緊自己興趣同盡量接觸多d事物 唔好浪費自己時間同埋唔好再次因為自己平時既懶惰令將來可能有既機會白白流失左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 俾首歌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tmmliJjsizc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtmmliJjsizc&d=FWZ%2FCQSRq5f4zfQNJOE280sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=a6f9fd2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tmmliJjsizc</a>"},{"pid":"fd887495501e9945b3ef674c00bfacc4b70f3cfc","tid":84790,"uid":15933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T18:49:07.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88da405399d8ae8495edde304bf6c76423d13416","tid":84790,"uid":67209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T18:50:13.000Z","msg":"加油呀ching"},{"pid":"3b963145ebd7ad76ad59d628976bd09c941c865c","tid":84790,"uid":68433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T18:51:15.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81e521598d2906c447f4f6ec903d1e021dc38a3e","tid":84790,"uid":40010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T18:57:43.000Z","msg":"同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ccafc552e42ecb9099dc0280f5346323f901872","tid":84790,"uid":74820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T19:01:17.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}